title: Technical Death Metal Essentials II
description:
TECHNICAL DEATH METAL

This is a collection of albums from prominent Technical Death Metal bands. Many of them are listed on the Wikipedia article on Technical Death Metal, and some were chosen by myself with the help of forums. This is part two of three on my series of Technical Death Metal Torrents. Part II contains more popular bands, as Part III will contain more obscure ones. The files may not be very organized. Some artists may be the same as in other Torrents, but the albums are different.

In this Torrent, you will find the albums:

Anata - Under A Stone With No Inscription
Arsis - We Are The Nightmare
Atheist - Unquestionable Presence
Beneath The Massacre - Dystopia
Brain Drill - Apocalyptic Feasting
Cryptopsy - None So Vile
